title: Back from HQ
description:
Kirk Minihane is back from his trip to New York City. Kirk recaps his experience with Jersey Jerry and the rest of the Barstool Sports crew. Mike Felger does not do jokes. Chris Klemmer is getting mentions from Big Cat and going all in on joining Barstool Sports. Dave Portnoy says he could produce a podcast himself, which appeared to irritate Eddie. It's official... Kirk Minihane and his brother are entering the Maine Mini Golf Open. A KMS swimsuit calendar and a trip to North Dakota may be in the works. Calls, Brandon Walker's top 10 SNL list & more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
